By the way,

579
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,560
I booked a restaurant

580
00:36:21,560 --> 00:36:23,140
to celebrate your birthday tonight.

581
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:24,840
Are you still thinking about this?

582
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:26,080
I told Nanting

583
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,860
we could eat at home.

584
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,260
Yes, let's eat at home. I'll cook.

585
00:36:30,710 --> 00:36:32,340
My mom told me

586
00:36:32,520 --> 00:36:34,450
to celebrate with auntie.

587
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:35,760
Thanks to her.

588
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:37,810
I bought you a scarf.

589
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:39,600
I planned to give it to you tonight.

590
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:41,320
Look, you're wasting money.

591
00:36:41,350 --> 00:36:42,390
I'm embarrassed.

592
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:43,750
This is what I should do.

593
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,980
You and Brother Nanting have been so nice to me since childhood.

594
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:47,970
I don't have any relatives or friends in Luzhou either.

595
00:36:47,970 --> 00:36:48,910
If you are willing,

596
00:36:48,910 --> 00:36:50,420
I'll celebrate your birthday with you in the future.

597
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,100
Okay.

598
00:36:52,690 --> 00:36:54,470
I still remember Brother Nanting

599
00:36:54,470 --> 00:36:56,220
celebrating my ten-year-old birthday with me.

600
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:57,120
That year in the amusement arcade

601
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:58,450
you caught a doll for me.

602
00:36:58,600 --> 00:36:59,790
I still keep it.

603
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:03,280
Really?

604
00:37:05,570 --> 00:37:07,900
Look at you. You can't remember anything.

605
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:08,910
He has been studying and playing basketball

606
00:37:08,910 --> 00:37:10,650
since childhood.

607
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:12,510
Now he only cares about work.

608
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,080
I'll reply to an email. You guys continue.

609
00:37:19,080 --> 00:37:21,190
You see, it comes again.

610
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:22,870
He's just a workaholic.

611
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:28,790
Auntie.

612
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,320
It's rare to come out today.

613
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,680
Let me take a photo for you.

614
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:32,110
Sure.

615
00:37:33,290 --> 00:37:33,970
-Come on.
-Come on.

616
00:37:33,970 --> 00:37:34,960
Let's keep it as a memento.

617
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:37,290
Are you done? Let's take a photo together.

618
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:38,440
Okay.

619
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:40,740
I'll shoot for you.

620
00:37:41,490 --> 00:37:43,080
Today is auntie's birthday.

621
00:37:43,080 --> 00:37:44,910
You two should take a photo together.

622
00:37:44,910 --> 00:37:45,910
We do it together.

623
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:47,690
Come on. Let's do it together.

624
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:51,040
I'll go for it.

625
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,050
Hello.

626
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,960
Can you take a photo for us?

627
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:56,520
Sure.

628
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:57,120
Thank you.

629
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:57,850
Thank you.

630
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:04,440
Here.

631
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,690
Three, two, one.

632
00:38:12,410 --> 00:38:14,830
I found this shop online.

633
00:38:15,310 --> 00:38:15,980
It's great.

634
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:18,220
Thank you.

635
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,170
You're welcome.

636
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:20,360
Thank you.

637
00:38:20,450 --> 00:38:21,380
You're welcome.

638
00:38:21,860 --> 00:38:24,120
Thank you for taking care of Polly for me.

639
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,570
Luckily, you chose Chinese food today.

640
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:28,110
I'm really not used to western food.

641
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:28,730
Me too.

642
00:38:29,050 --> 00:38:30,510
Every time I fly abroad and eat western food,

643
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:31,350
I feel upset.

644
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:32,840
As soon as I come back,

645
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,040
I'll have a bowl of porridge first.

646
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:36,060
You can buy me porridge today.

647
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,120
No way.

648
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:38,210
I must show my sincerity

649
00:38:38,210 --> 00:38:39,540
to treat Mr. Ni to a meal.

650
00:38:40,250 --> 00:38:42,000
Then I'll study the menu

651
00:38:42,220 --> 00:38:44,020
and order something expensive.

652
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:46,160
Don't be too expensive. It's enough.

653
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,280
Order whatever you want.

654
00:39:58,770 --> 00:39:59,280
Song,

655
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:03,250
do you want to play games or watch TV?

656
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,300
-I…
-No.

657
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:06,860
Did I disturb you?

658
00:40:07,140 --> 00:40:07,650
No.

659
00:40:11,250 --> 00:40:12,110
This is for you.

660
00:40:13,580 --> 00:40:14,740
For me?

661
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,270
There was an event in the mall today.

662
00:40:18,270 --> 00:40:20,530
I got the perfume when I bought the socks.

663
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:25,480
When I opened it, it was a lady's perfume.

664
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,180
I...

665
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:28,050
I don't have a girlfriend either.

666
00:40:28,050 --> 00:40:29,250
So I'll give it to you.

667
00:40:40,750 --> 00:40:41,600
Well...

668
00:40:42,020 --> 00:40:43,220
thank you.

669
00:40:45,010 --> 00:40:45,940
You're welcome.

670
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,560
Open it and see if you like it.

671
00:40:59,290 --> 00:41:00,120
It's good.

672
00:41:00,410 --> 00:41:01,060
Thank you.

673
00:41:01,120 --> 00:41:02,250
I'm glad you like it.

674
00:41:03,410 --> 00:41:05,400
I'll take another person's shift tomorrow morning.

675
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:06,330
I'm going to bed.

676
00:41:07,170 --> 00:41:08,630
You should rest early too.

677
00:41:55,850 --> 00:41:56,490
I'm sorry.

678
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:57,260
