680
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:10,380
Cheng Xiao?

681
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:12,780
Cheng Xiao?

682
00:42:14,070 --> 00:42:14,870
Brother Zhan.

683
00:42:16,820 --> 00:42:18,020
What did you just say?

684
00:42:18,410 --> 00:42:19,460
Wang Fan called me.

685
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:21,080
I need to go back to the hangar.

686
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:21,670
Okay.

687
00:42:22,010 --> 00:42:22,550
I'm sorry.

688
00:42:22,550 --> 00:42:24,550
I couldn't take you home every time.

689
00:42:24,810 --> 00:42:26,550
It's okay. Work is more important.

690
00:42:26,550 --> 00:42:27,800
I'll pay the bill first.

691
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:29,530
I won't stand on ceremony then.

692
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:30,930
Thank you for your attendance, Mr. Ni.
